  comparison table; say "Full library" instead so the copy doesn't
  need updating every time the widget count changes.
- Clarify the Org-creation cell ("Requires company email" instead of
  a bare "Company email" that didn't read as a value on its own).
- Regroup the flat 12-row table into Usage / Sharing & embedding /
  Collaboration sections with divider rows, swap the plain checkmark
  text for Check/X icons, highlight the Pro column with a tinted
  background, and show each plan's price under its name in the header.

